{"tid":539592,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港大民主牆現粗口字句　辱罵浸大校長錢大康","createTime":"2018-01-24T16:25:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-25T12:16:48.000Z","uid":20933,"like":106,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"76acac4c805036b427d4a90b099717e42d550a1d","tid":539592,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T16:25:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180124/s00001/94da5ef4be2f46a36aeaec3e5a183cb0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180124%2Fs00001%2F94da5ef4be2f46a36aeaec3e5a183cb0.jpg&h=8c822af7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「香港大學學生會學苑即時新聞」fb今晚貼文，港大民主牆今晚出現不少聲援浸大抗議學生，和批評浸大校長錢大康的字句，包括有粗言字句的「錢大康我X你老母」、「校方打壓可恥，聲援浸大學生」、「不要港版萬壽臺（朝鮮部分學術機構的名字）」，等等。<br />\n<br />\n錢大康今天宣布，要兩名被指在早前抗議普通話豁免試風波中，涉及粗言辱罵的學生即時停學。錢大康轉職浸大前，原任港大首席副校長。<br />\n<br />\n另外，中大校園電台fb亦指，星期三晚約11時，中大民主牆出現字句，辱罵浸大校長錢大康，及有份決定對學生停學處分的學生輔導長鄧裕南，當中包括「錢大康我X你老竇校方打壓可恥　未審先判言不慚皇天擊殺鄧裕南」。"},{"pid":"e0d8b8aa56885f00515350d07f365c07c6b7b6ba","tid":539592,"uid":152437,"like":66,"dislike":1,"score":65,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T16:38:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4f315fe36aae72955775b22200d10cf78e66650e","tid":539592,"uid":105924,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T16:56:43.000Z","msg":"錢大康我屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a21bfa8c703a1d7d898cb52d6d15537ea0d05903","tid":539592,"uid":118120,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T16:58:44.000Z","msg":"錢大康我愛你老母 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84ad4860e4bd829701b54de59e5d434c43fa3662","tid":539592,"uid":14912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T16:59:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>錢大康我愛你老母</blockquote>"},{"pid":"bbcf1c6c2ffa8010e89a924db12b623497810ef4","tid":539592,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T17:17:53.000Z","msg":"錢大康我屌你老母"},{"pid"